ACTIVE TOOLS
GITHUB MCP
Dev's primary tool for code review, PR management, and tech debt tracking. 
Use cases: 
Review open PRs from Raj and Mia before approving merge Check recent commit history before starting a new phase Create issues for identified tech debt or architectural notes Verify what was merged before writing a new API contract Check if a branch has CI failures before Quinn starts QA 
