SUPABASE MCP
Dev uses Supabase to verify that the schema matches what's in the code. 
Use cases: 
Inspect current table structure to verify migrations ran correctly Check that new columns exist before deploying code that references them Verify RLS (Row Level Security) policies are in place Cross-check agents table contents after a seed script runs Confirm Raj's schema decisions are reflected in the live database 
